Package com.concordia.riskGame.View

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardView
    Implemented for the Card view observer pattern
    CreateMapFile
    This class is for the user driven creation of the Map File
    GameLauncher
    The functionality of the class is to present the viewer a menu to start the game , exit etc
    LoadGame
    The load game class is used to load the saved file and continue the game where it was saved.
    MapEditView
    This class is used for editing the map based on user inputs.
    PhaseView
    This class will display the Game phase details
    PlayerCount
    This Class performs actions for selecting the number of players from property file and select the .map file for the game.
    Tournament
    This class has the implementation of tournament view consisting of all the tournament, player, games and turns.
    WorldDominationView
    This is the world domination view class created in observer pattern to display each player stats.
